sequenceDiagram
    participant App as App Code
    participant HUD as HUD
    participant CV as ContentView
    participant BG as BackgroundView
    participant Anim as Animation

    App->>HUD: show(to: view, mode: .indicator)
    activate HUD
    HUD->>BG: Configure background style
    HUD->>CV: Configure content (indicator, labels)
    HUD->>Anim: Begin show animation
    Anim-->>HUD: Animation complete

    Note over App,Anim: HUD is visible

    App->>HUD: Update progress / label
    HUD->>CV: Update content views

    App->>HUD: hide(animated: true)
    HUD->>Anim: Begin hide animation
    Anim-->>HUD: Animation complete
    HUD->>HUD: removeFromSuperview()
    HUD-->>App: completionBlock()
    deactivate HUD
